@startuml
hide empty description
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #F5F5F5
  BorderColor #333333
}

[*] --> Approach

state "Acercamiento\n(Approach)" as Approach
state "Huida\n(Escape)" as Escape
state "Disparo\n(Shoot)" as Shoot

Approach -right-> Escape : dist < 4 u
Approach --> Shoot : 4 u ≤ dist ≤ 12 u
Escape -left-> Approach : dist > 12 u
Escape -right-> Shoot : 4 u ≤ dist ≤ 12 u
Shoot -left-> Escape : dist < 4 u
Shoot --> Approach : dist > 12 u
@enduml
